<number box="[857,871,624,647]" pageId="72" pageNumber="73" value="7.0">7</number>
th tergite triangular, with basal apodeme extending for ⅔ of the length of the 
<number box="[468,482,661,686]" pageId="72" pageNumber="73" value="6.0">6</number>
